{"tid":2236320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：「坦克車」事件  沈旭暉稱唔知「捐贈」（李八方）","createTime":"2020-10-09T11:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T11:21:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac32213f2b032205f9e48e228dfaa2e6eda5323","tid":2236320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/Y7XJ6EQXFVF2HATGMHBC5T6VKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FY7XJ6EQXFVF2HATGMHBC5T6VKU%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=a8ca7edb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FY7XJ6EQXFVF2HATGMHBC5T6VKU%2F&h=836480e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/Y7XJ6EQXFVF2HATGMHBC5T6VKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：「坦克車」事件 <br />\n沈旭暉稱唔知「捐贈」（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/01pLqpKUCfUWAEoMvsDtvfpuSBM=/1258x871/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IZ4EZZ5N2JCN7OY4XMQM46F3L4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F01pLqpKUCfUWAEoMvsDtvfpuSBM%3D%2F1258x871%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIZ4EZZ5N2JCN7OY4XMQM46F3L4.jpg&h=d3c8ab09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■沈旭暉於fb專頁內對王百羽事件作出了回應。<br />\n<br />\n八方噚日寫綽號「超區坦克車」嘅本土派元朗區議員王百羽，使咗接近485萬元選舉開支，當中超過450萬元嘅選舉服務同貨品由U Made This公司捐贈，而呢間公司大股東，就係學者沈旭暉創辦嘅GLOS Company Limited，令人覺得沈旭暉係王百羽金主，但奇就奇在，沈旭暉話自己完全唔知呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司董事引咎請辭<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉噚日接受有線訪問，話完全唔知名下子公司有董事接呢張單，自己都有啲驚訝，又話佢自己幫候選人做YouTube訪問，都只係收街坊價二千幾蚊。<br />\n<br />\n佢自言都覺得張單入面有啲服務收費唔合理，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}